==Relocating a house==
Estate agents can move a POH from its starting location in [[Rimmington]] to any of the other [[house portal]]s locations identified by the portal icon ([[File:House portal icon.png]]) on the [[minimap]]. These locations include [[Rimmington]], [[Taverley]], [[Pollnivneach]], [[Hosidius]], [[Rellekka]], [[Brimhaven]], [[Yanille]], and [[Prifddinas]].

